Before you can connect Alexa with RoboZone robot, please follow steps below:
a. Download "RoboZone" app from Google Play or App Store;
b. Sign up or sign in with your RoboZone App account;
c. Setup the device with your "RoboZone" app, and make sure you can control it by the app;
d. Search "RoboZone" skill and link account;
e. When setup is ready,try ask “Alexa” to control your devices.
